                                <div class="region-guide-content">
                                    <p><strong>国际大一课程</strong></p>
                                    <p>该课程有时称为文凭课程，等同于本科学位一年级课程。完成此课程后，你可进入所选大学的本科学位二年级就读。</p>
                                </div>
                                <a title="International Year One in Business" class="l-cta cta" href="/zh-cn/study-programs?icsregion=uk&amp;icsdiscipline=business_and_management&amp;icslevel=international_year_one_(international_year_two_in_scotland)#coursetool">查找商科国际大一课程</a>
                            </div>
                            <div class="region-guide anim-on-scroll anim-fade-in-slide-up">
                                <div class="region-guide-content">
                                    <p><strong>研究生文凭课程或硕士预科课程</strong></p>
                                    <p>硕士文凭或硕士预科课程可帮助你做好进入英国大学攻读研究生阶段学位课程学习的准备。</p>
                                </div>
                                <a title="Graduate Diploma in Business" class="l-cta cta" href="/zh-cn/study-programs?icsregion=uk&amp;icsdiscipline=business_and_management&amp;icslevel=graduate_diploma/pre-masters#coursetool">查找商科研究生文凭课程</a>
                            </div>
